title: Room Full of Mirrors - Jimi Hendrix Biography (1hr segments)
description:
Room Full of Mirrors: A Biography of Jimi Hendrix is a 2005 biography of the influential rock guitarist, singer, and songwriter Jimi Hendrix. It was written by Charles R. Cross

Originally published: August 15, 2005

Author: Charles R. Cross

Genres: Biography

Page count: 384 (13:30:33 Read time)

Publisher: Sceptre

Country: United States of America

This 13+ Hr book has been broken up into 14 1 hour files since that better fits some people's listening options.

I also have the entire 13 hour mp3 on one file... if you want that torrent is uploaded as well!

An amazing book on a remarkable person in an interesting era... I highly recommend it!
